title: The Cabin in the Woods
description:
Our story tonight is called “The Cabin in the Woods” and it’s a story about a trip along winding roads and a special place at the end of them. It’s also about pine cones high in their branches, a jigsaw puzzle spread out on the kitchen table and calm quiet feeling that comes from being far away from everything.

So get cozy and ready to sleep.

Order the book now! hyperurl.co/NothingMuchHappens

This episode mentions alcohol.
